reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 323/92: ZONING AREAS - UNORGANIZED TOWNSHIP OF CATHCART, DISTRICT OF KENORA
reg_info.reg_name_text: Zoning Areas — Unorganized Township of Cathcart, District of Kenora
reg_info.citation: O. Reg. 323/92: ZONING AREAS - UNORGANIZED TOWNSHIP OF CATHCART, DISTRICT OF KENORA
reg_info.act_under: Planning Act   Loi sur l’aménagement du territoire

content.content: 1. In this Order, “motel unit” means one or more habitable rooms with separate kitchen and sanitary facilities for the exclusive use of the occupants and with a private entrance from outside the motel structure. O. Reg. 323/92, s. 1.
content.raw_html:
1. In this Order,

“motel unit” means one or more habitable rooms with separate kitchen and sanitary facilities for the exclusive use of the occupants and with a private entrance from outside the motel structure. O. Reg. 323/92, s. 1.

content.content: 2. This Order applies to those lands in the geographic Township of Cathcart in the District of Kenora being part of Location HM III and designated as Part 1 on Plan 23R-4034 registered in the Land Registry Office for the Land Titles Division of Kenora (No. 23). O. Reg. 323/92, s. 2.
content.raw_html: 2. This Order applies to those lands in the geographic Township of Cathcart in the District of Kenora being part of Location HM III and designated as Part 1 on Plan 23R-4034 registered in the Land Registry Office for the Land Titles Division of Kenora (No. 23). O. Reg. 323/92, s. 2.

content.content: 3. No land to which this Order applies shall be used and no building or structure shall be erected, located or used on the land except in accordance with this Order. O. Reg. 323/92, s. 3.
content.raw_html: 3. No land to which this Order applies shall be used and no building or structure shall be erected, located or used on the land except in accordance with this Order. O. Reg. 323/92, s. 3.

content.content:
4. Every use of land and every erection, location or use of buildings or structures on the land is prohibited except the location and use of a mobile structure used or intended to be used as a motel together with accessory buildings and structures if the following requirements are met:  Maximum number of motel units   6 

  Maximum ground floor area   223 square metres 

  Maximum height   3 metres O. Reg. 323/92, s. 4.
content.raw_html:
4. Every use of land and every erection, location or use of buildings or structures on the land is prohibited except the location and use of a mobile structure used or intended to be used as a motel together with accessory buildings and structures if the following requirements are met:

 

Maximum number of motel units

6

Maximum ground floor area

223 square metres

Maximum height

3 metres

O. Reg. 323/92, s. 4.
